parent1.code: A watercolor of a resplendent golden phoenix with magnificent radiant feathers in the style of vibrant abstract expressionism. It elegantly perches on the rugged edge of a craggy cliff overlooking a vast, serene desert under a stunning twilight sky, casting an enchanting warm glow from its wings, amidst a surreal landscape of towering wind-carved rock formations and mesmerizing floating glass orbs.

offspring.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with radiant feathers in the style of vibrant Impressionism. It majestically soars above the crystalline ocean on a clear day, teeming with luminescent sea creatures amidst towering bioluminescent coral reefs and glowing jellyfish.
